data.description: Like new, story and a half Brick, stone, and vinyl home that has a $40,000 energy efficiency package installed by previous owner. The Electric bill is $10.00 per month. Beautiful Great room with 20'ft. ceilings and gas log fireplace with built-in cabinets. and solid surface countertops. Great room and dining room have wainscoting and coffered ceilings. Gourmet kitchen with island pantry, upgraded double stacked cabinets, and stainless appliances. Main level laundry room with cabinets and sink. Master bedroom suite, double trey ceilings, his and hers closets, huge lavish master bath with double sinks and walk in shower. Two other main level bedrooms and bath, a walk up floored attic with additional 700 +/- sq. ft. for future expansion. It is already roughed in for 3rd bath. Other features include freshly painted Great Room & Dining Room, hardwood & tiled floors, 2 car garage, beautifully landscaped, fenced in backyard, concrete driveway, and screened in porch.
